WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.310
Good morning family, how are y'all

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:05.030
doing? I have a video to

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:07.030
tell you all about a dream I had two

00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:10.390
nights ago. This is how the

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.110
dream goes; I'll just get right to it

00:00:12.110 --> 00:00:12.120
because

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:14.629
I don't want to waste your time.

00:00:14.639 --> 00:00:18.150
In the dream, I was sleeping

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:22.349
and I wake up,

00:00:22.359 --> 00:00:25.109
looking out the window at my

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:28.550
house. I pick up my phone and I see

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:31.550
all these news bulletins on my phone

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:34.069
from YouTube, and friends

00:00:34.069 --> 00:00:34.079
were

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:37.069
trying to tell me what was going on.

00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:40.229
I

00:00:40.239 --> 00:00:43.630
start seeing that there is a major

00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:45.510
announcement by the United States

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:49.750
government. I see the president, but

00:00:49.760 --> 00:00:53.029
in this dream, it's

00:00:53.039 --> 00:00:55.389
President Trump again. President

00:00:55.399 --> 00:00:59.349
Trump is holding a podium with the

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:02.950
presidential seal on it, and he

00:01:02.960 --> 00:01:04.910
starts talking. He has a blue

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:08.830
suit on with a white shirt and a red tie,

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:11.310
just like he usually

00:01:11.320 --> 00:01:13.190
wears, but it was a really

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:16.270
bright blue suit. He was very

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:20.350
somber in his face and he said, 'My

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:23.350
fellow Americans.'Basically, he says,

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:25.789
'I have an announcement to make;

00:01:25.799 --> 00:01:26.990
there's another

00:01:26.990 --> 00:01:27.000
virus.'He

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:30.230
starts explaining to

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:33.630
everybody that this virus is

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:37.230
basically a new virus that is

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:41.069
going to dwarf COVID, making COVID look

00:01:41.079 --> 00:01:43.270
like it was a wimpy virus compared to

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:46.030
what this new virus is. The death

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:50.830
ratio was skyrocketing, even higher

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:55.749
than COVID did. This started in

00:01:55.759 --> 00:01:58.230
Europe, which was interesting, and he was

00:01:58.240 --> 00:02:00.950
making an announcement that we

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:05.190
were going on lockdowns again

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:10.070
instantaneously. I felt like, 'Oh no,

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:13.589
this is what I saw.'In my dream,

00:02:13.599 --> 00:02:16.150
I'm thinking, 'This is what the Lord

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:18.589
showed me. This is the virus that I've

00:02:18.599 --> 00:02:21.990
warned you all about, and here it

00:02:21.990 --> 00:02:22.000
comes.'I

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.830
was thinking in

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:28.509
the dream that I'm not prepared

00:02:28.519 --> 00:02:31.670
enough and need to get more supplies. He was

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:34.949
calling for a major lockdown,

00:02:34.959 --> 00:02:38.470
calling for no international flights

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:42.070
coming in or going out. He was telling

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:44.790
everybody that we were going on

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:46.430
another lockdown, like an extended

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:50.550
lockdown for 20-some days to stop the spread

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.710
because there were some cases in America, specifically

00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:52.720
in

00:02:52.720 --> 00:02:56.470
the

00:02:56.470 --> 00:02:56.480
Northeast.

00:02:56.480 --> 00:03:00.070
He was taking

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:03.030
precautions to lock everything

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:05.470
down because of what was happening

00:03:05.480 --> 00:03:08.270
overseas. People were

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:10.470
perishing, like I told you all, and they

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:13.670
were heavy-set, obese people.

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:15.990
I just remember

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:19.990
watching the news in the dream and then

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:22.309
when he made the announcement that we

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:24.550
were going on lockdowns again,

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:27.430
people panicked. They were

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:29.309
hitting the grocery stores

00:03:29.309 --> 00:03:29.319
and

00:03:29.319 --> 00:03:32.190
the Walmart Superstores,

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:34.550
wiping stuff out

00:03:34.550 --> 00:03:34.560
and

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:37.190
buying everything

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:39.030
they could get their hands on. It

00:03:39.030 --> 00:03:39.040
was

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:41.910
almost like people were

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:45.270
in a panic because of what they had

00:03:45.270 --> 00:03:45.280
already

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:47.710
lived through. They already

00:03:47.710 --> 00:03:47.720
knew

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:51.910
what was coming, so people were acting

00:03:51.920 --> 00:03:54.309
crazy in the grocery stores. It wasn't just

00:03:54.319 --> 00:03:56.110
about toilet paper this time; it was

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:58.309
about everything—chips, whatever they

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:00.710
could get their hands

00:04:00.710 --> 00:04:00.720
on—filling

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:02.550
their buggies.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.750
It was that way for

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:08.350
everything. I remember

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:12.149
watching the news in

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:14.429
the dream—it was such a weird

00:04:14.439 --> 00:04:16.509
dream—with

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:19.629
all the major news

00:04:19.639 --> 00:04:22.310
networks talking about this being a new

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:25.710
virus and a new pandemic.

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:29.430
They kept

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:31.390
saying in their speech

00:04:31.390 --> 00:04:31.400
that

00:04:31.400 --> 00:04:34.950
the death toll ratio is going to

00:04:34.950 --> 00:04:34.960
dwarf

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:39.430
COVID.

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:42.749
Basically, that was the dream, but I

00:04:42.759 --> 00:04:45.629
just remember feeling

00:04:45.639 --> 00:04:48.230
uneasy because of what the

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:50.830
Lord had shown me prophetically already

00:04:50.840 --> 00:04:54.150
prior to the dream, warning you all.

00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:57.430
It was just

00:04:57.440 --> 00:05:00.469
very eerie.

00:05:00.469 --> 00:05:00.479
I

00:05:00.479 --> 00:05:02.830
wanted to come on and tell you all that.

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:05.710
I know

00:05:05.710 --> 00:05:05.720
you'll

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:07.270
probably say, 'Oh, it was just

00:05:07.280 --> 00:05:09.629
a dream,'but I don't have

00:05:09.639 --> 00:05:11.590
dreams like that

00:05:11.590 --> 00:05:11.600
often.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:13.870
When the Lord talks to

00:05:13.880 --> 00:05:15.550
me, I know it when I wake up and I

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:18.230
remember things.

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:20.350
He's speaking to me through that

00:05:20.350 --> 00:05:20.360
to say,

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:23.189
'Here it is again, I'm

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:25.950
warning

00:05:25.950 --> 00:05:25.960
you.'I

00:05:25.960 --> 00:05:27.430
almost didn't even say

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:29.350
anything about it, but I felt like I

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:30.230
should

00:05:30.230 --> 00:05:30.240
because

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:32.590
I'm a Watchman. If

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:34.909
you think this is just because I

00:05:34.919 --> 00:05:37.029
had some bad Chinese

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:39.710
food that

00:05:39.710 --> 00:05:39.720
night—which

00:05:39.720 --> 00:05:42.029
I don't eat

00:05:42.029 --> 00:05:42.039
anyway—you

00:05:42.039 --> 00:05:44.230
could just take it and

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:46.189
put it on a shelf. But I felt

00:05:46.199 --> 00:05:48.150
in my heart it was serious

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:50.950
enough to tell you all. I

00:05:50.960 --> 00:05:52.710
thought it was cool because Trump was

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:54.830
behind the

00:05:54.840 --> 00:05:58.350
podium talking, not Biden, so

00:05:58.360 --> 00:06:00.430
that was interesting. It was

00:06:00.440 --> 00:06:02.909
in the spring again;

00:06:02.919 --> 00:06:05.469
I could see the leaves on the trees

00:06:05.479 --> 00:06:08.150
coming out. It was just like

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:10.189
whenever they locked everything

00:06:10.199 --> 00:06:13.309
down with COVID in the spring, and they were

00:06:13.319 --> 00:06:15.670
doing it again. But this time it

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:17.990
did not start in Asia; it started in Europe—England,

00:06:17.990 --> 00:06:18.000
France,

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:21.830
and all that

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:24.990
over there. It

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.749
was already going on before, so

00:06:27.759 --> 00:06:29.710
people were watching it. Then

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:31.390
he made the announcement. It looked

00:06:31.400 --> 00:06:33.990
like it was weeks prior,

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.950
similar to COVID, but I thought it was

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:38.629
interesting that there were no

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:40.510
flights. He said he was locking down all

00:06:40.520 --> 00:06:43.150
air traffic,

00:06:43.150 --> 00:06:43.160
and

00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:46.550
I even perceived that

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:49.870
they were locking down

00:06:49.880 --> 00:06:52.230
state-to-state travel, not

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:54.830
allowing people to travel by airplane between

00:06:54.830 --> 00:06:54.840
states,

00:06:54.840 --> 00:06:57.350
which I think would be

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.629
over the top. But that's what I

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:01.510
was seeing—they were locking down

00:07:01.520 --> 00:07:04.230
airplanes

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:06.510
because it was an airborne

00:07:06.520 --> 00:07:09.430
virus, not spread by fluids.

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:11.589
I'm not coming on

00:07:11.599 --> 00:07:14.070
to try to scare y'all; I come on here

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:16.469
to warn you so you can take it

00:07:16.479 --> 00:07:19.550
and pray over it with me.

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:21.749
It really is heavy

00:07:21.759 --> 00:07:23.350
because I've been

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:25.589
feeling it, praying over things and

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:27.629
interceding over what I've warned you

00:07:27.639 --> 00:07:29.670
about. I just want to pray

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:31.550
for you all today.

00:07:35.479 --> 00:07:38.749
Father, I just thank you, Lord,

00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:42.670
for every single warning you give us. You

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:45.149
never want us to be caught off guard,

00:07:45.159 --> 00:07:49.629
in fear, worry,

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:52.790
or torment. Father, you're a good

00:07:52.800 --> 00:07:55.589
Father and you warn us of what's

00:07:55.599 --> 00:07:58.670
to come. I thank you, Father, that we

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:00.110
are

00:08:00.110 --> 00:08:00.120
prepared—not

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:03.149
just physically and mentally, but

00:08:03.149 --> 00:08:03.159
spiritually—that

00:08:03.159 --> 00:08:05.790
we

00:08:05.800 --> 00:08:09.430
know who we are in Christ. We take our

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:11.990
authority and our rightful place

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:14.830
seated next to you, and we use

00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:17.510
that authority against all sickness

00:08:17.510 --> 00:08:17.520
and

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:20.189
disease. You said in your

00:08:20.199 --> 00:08:22.790
word, Lord, that a thousand should fall at

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:25.430
our side and 10,000 at our right hand, but

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:28.550
it would not come nigh us. Father, I thank

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:31.070
you, Lord, that if this virus was to

00:08:31.080 --> 00:08:34.070
come about—and I pray it

00:08:34.070 --> 00:08:34.080
doesn't—but

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:36.350
if it did, we

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:39.790
have Psalm 91 and Psalm 23.

00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:42.070
You've warned me several

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:44.310
times that there was a storm coming; you

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:47.110
warned me about this virus—I think

00:08:47.120 --> 00:08:48.710
this is the third time now

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.269
you've talked to me about this, even in

00:08:50.279 --> 00:08:53.910
my dreams. I thank you, Father, that you

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:56.190
protect us. I thank you, Lord, that our

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.389
angels will bear us up in their hands

00:08:58.399 --> 00:09:01.069
lest we dash our foot against a stone. I

00:09:01.079 --> 00:09:02.550
thank you, Father, that we're doing what

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:04.949
it takes to take care of our

00:09:04.949 --> 00:09:04.959
flesh—getting

00:09:04.959 --> 00:09:06.750
the weight off,

00:09:06.760 --> 00:09:08.790
exercising, and honoring our

00:09:08.790 --> 00:09:08.800
temples—that

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:10.910
we are

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:14.269
physically fit and will live long and

00:09:14.279 --> 00:09:17.150
finish strong. I plead the blood of Jesus

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:19.630
over every single one of us. I thank

00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:23.069
you, Father, that you have our future;

00:09:23.079 --> 00:09:25.230
you know our future more than we know

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:27.670
our past, and you have a plan for our

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:30.230
lives. Father, I thank you for saying, 'Beloved, I

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:32.350
wish above all things that you prosper

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:35.269
and be in health, even as your soul

00:09:35.269 --> 00:09:35.279
prospers.'I

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:37.670
thank you, Father, that we

00:09:37.680 --> 00:09:40.110
are prosperous in our spirit, soul, and

00:09:40.110 --> 00:09:40.120
body—mentally,

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:42.870
emotionally, physically,

00:09:42.870 --> 00:09:42.880
and

00:09:42.880 --> 00:09:46.910
financially. We are sound in

00:09:46.910 --> 00:09:46.920
Jesus'name.

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:48.710
I thank you, Lord, that Trump would

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:51.350
win instead of Joe Biden. I plead the

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:54.430
blood of Jesus over our nation,

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:56.269
that we'd have godly leadership. If we

00:09:56.279 --> 00:09:57.949
were to go into something like this

00:09:57.959 --> 00:09:59.870
again, we would have somebody in

00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:01.829
there with some sense,

00:10:01.829 --> 00:10:01.839
leading

00:10:01.839 --> 00:10:04.150
this country

00:10:04.150 --> 00:10:04.160
and

00:10:04.160 --> 00:10:06.910
knowing how to

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:08.790
help us, doing a

00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:11.110
better job than they did last time.

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:13.870
Father, I thank you that

00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:16.949
we're not going to be afraid of

00:10:16.959 --> 00:10:20.310
whatever comes because we trust you. We

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.430
confidently trust in the finished work

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:25.069
of Jesus Christ, that he paid the price

00:10:25.079 --> 00:10:28.150
for us to walk in victory over sickness,

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:31.389
disease, death, and all

00:10:31.399 --> 00:10:33.630
torment of fear. It doesn't

00:10:33.640 --> 00:10:35.870
matter, God; I know that you have a plan

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:38.230
for our lives and a plan for

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:40.550
these people on this YouTube channel. I

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:42.990
bless them in the name of

00:10:42.990 --> 00:10:43.000
Jesus—every

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:44.430
single one of them, their

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.870
marriages, their children,

00:10:46.870 --> 00:10:46.880
and

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:49.150
their houses. Father, in the

00:10:49.160 --> 00:10:53.269
name of Jesus, you are our Father

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:56.030
and we love you. We know you love

00:10:56.040 --> 00:10:59.670
us, and in Jesus'name, we pray. Amen.

00:10:59.680 --> 00:11:02.829
Amen. So, I hope this

00:11:02.839 --> 00:11:04.910
blessed you today. I just felt like you

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:07.990
should know. I appreciate it if

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:12.470
you could like my video to

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:15.509
help us with the algorithm. Comment

00:11:15.519 --> 00:11:17.910
down below if you've had dreams about a

00:11:17.920 --> 00:11:19.829
new virus

00:11:19.829 --> 00:11:19.839
or

00:11:19.839 --> 00:11:21.910
if the Lord's warned

00:11:21.920 --> 00:11:24.389
you about something

00:11:24.399 --> 00:11:27.750
more deadly than COVID. I ask you

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:29.870
to be polite in the comments section;

00:11:29.880 --> 00:11:33.269
don't be

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:35.269
rude, let's just be friends.

00:11:35.279 --> 00:11:38.430
I

00:11:38.440 --> 00:11:40.629
appreciate all y'all's support. God bless

00:11:40.639 --> 00:11:43.269
you guys; put a smile on your face

00:11:43.279 --> 00:11:46.910
and let God bless you all. I might

00:11:46.920 --> 00:11:50.389
say 'guys'because

00:11:50.389 --> 00:11:50.399
I

00:11:50.399 --> 00:11:52.990
forget the ladies; I don't mean to, sorry.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:55.150
Put a smile on your face and a song in

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:57.870
your heart. Jesus loves you so much and

00:11:57.880 --> 00:11:59.750
we love you, and we will see you next

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:03.920
time. Y'all have a blessed day. Bye-bye.

